commit.message: Update changelog and noxfile

add contains to gha workflow
- also install diagrams for mypy
improve graph handling for deeply nested states
fix diagram test  and pgv node_style

fix roi_state in graphviz
- maintain unions for active state

test imports in test_diagrams
- removed some unused code
matrix variable had wrong name [gha]
add mypy config

move graphviz to diagrams requirement;
- adjust noxfile
make diagrams install an extra step [gha]
extend diagrams testing
add 2.7 to nox

switch to nox
- add noxfile
- update MANIFEST

moving to nox
- deleting tox.ini

changes to diagrams
- anchors are called like their parent state (_anchor-prefix) was removed
- improve support for parallel states

Remove surrounding whitespace from docstrings

Closes #599
test locked function reference labeling; improve output
Add event to __repr__ of EventData
extend testing for nested state with custom separator
do not cover core ImportError (py2)

mark routes for Py3.4 and earlier as not covered

will be remove in the next major release

Remove Python 3.7 from pytest.yml

Literals were introduced in 3.8 and will cause mypy to fail.

Update CI `test` job

Update supported Python versions and version of Github actions
Add `.venv` to gitignore

Add remark about auto-transitions (#631)

If you follow the documentation from the start, get_triggers will return auto transitions which might not be expected behaviour.
